## [1.0.0] – Core Release
**Date:** 2026-01-20

### Added
- OpenIMMS System Manual (Level-1 manufacturing system definition)
- OpenIMMS Validation Model (IQ–OQ–PQ, risk-based)
- Scientific Injection Moulding (SIM) Framework
- Risk–Parameter Traceability Matrix (ISO 14971 integration)
- Governance model
- Creative Commons Attribution–ShareAlike 4.0 license
- Public README and project structure
- Validation Master Plan (VMP) template for OpenIMMS adoption

### Notes
- This release defines the core OpenIMMS framework.
- No backward compatibility guarantees prior to this version.
